    public class MixedRowTable<Bean,Model extends MixedRowTableModel & BeanTableModel<Bean>>
extends DecoratedTable<Bean,Model>
    A table that displays rows in groups. The ordering of the rows within each group is constant but sorting and filtering can be applied to the groups. Row groups are visually separated by alternating background colors (rows within a group have the same background color).
